{"tid":1255033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨: 不覺得道歉會變成「風土病」","createTime":"2019-06-24T10:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T03:15:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"17b4cc6b6bf63cbcd72f18ce5ab35c015b5eea59","tid":1255033,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"月底離任的港鐵主席馬時亨表示，要令港鐵以後不加價，唯一辦法是變成由政府全資擁有公司，但這種做法，可能為港鐵帶來「財力無，機器壞，服務水平降低」的風險。<br />\n<br />\n任內曾就沙中綫工程管理問題向市民致歉，馬時亨說，不覺得道歉會變成「風土病」。至於道歉是否真誠，他認為，每個人心裡都有一把尺衡量。"},{"pid":"e871569098e0672d7fc2adac57c254ab48a7cfee","tid":1255033,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"政府把尺一向特別唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86819541ceec398ade90fcd605ac902253046fcd","tid":1255033,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"我話ok就ok&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;錄音機式道歉"},{"pid":"614c1c2ffc290765ae75031f3c93b0ffeb81987d","tid":1255033,"uid":40867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"係政府咁無能要道歉姐<br />\n睇下我馬主席八面威風 我話OK就OK<br />\n加埋你價都得啊"},{"pid":"b279e16093bb53abbd030bd15fd1b2a6212be4f9","tid":1255033,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T03:15:47.000Z","msg":"我話OK 就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}